reviewText: Who could not love Roy Rogers?  A glamorous cowboy with a beautiful horse and a charming wife.  An energetic western with loving, family overtones.  The good guy in the days of old.

There are several Roy Rogers movies on VHS that are listed as being in color when they are not.  This is one of them.  They are made by Alpha Omega Publications and are dated Oct. 19th, 2004.  This movie is in B&W and not in color.
